{"tid":2348559,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"關注周末預約睇樓升3.1%, 買家願意追價, 港島屋苑成交較上月多三成","createTime":"2020-12-31T19:22:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T03:31:23.000Z","uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eabc89a36fd10e712fa2a4fd002fe05f431b095e","tid":2348559,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T19:22:12.000Z","msg":"50屋苑周末預約睇樓升3.1%<br />\n<br />\n利嘉閣地產研究部主管陳海潮表示，近日樓市買賣氣氛相對平穩，而元旦長假期買家、業主大都留港迎新歲，<span class=\"red\"><strong>利好</strong></span>二手屋苑預約睇樓活動。根據利嘉閣地產研究部數據估算，全港50個指標屋苑共錄1,180組客戶於周末預約睇樓，按周上<span class=\"red\"><strong>升</strong></span>3.1%，而<strong><span class=\"red\">三天長假則約有1,565組客戶。本港置業需求強勁</span></strong>，....料隨疫情緩和，發展商加快推盤，樓市交投氣氛可望重燃。<br />\n<br />\n港島區8個指標屋苑於周末暫錄215組客戶預約睇樓，按周微增2.4%，而元旦長假則約有285組客戶。利嘉閣地產逸樺園一行高級經理吳玉蘭表示，臨近新年，康怡花園睇樓及交投氣氛不俗，當中有置業需求的準買家，屋苑<span class=\"red\"><strong>樓價始終堅挺</strong></span>，開始按捺不住入市，並有個別<strong><span class=\"red\">買家願意追價</span></strong>，令近日有優質單位以理想價成交，反映買家對後市保持信心。本月康怡花園暫錄約17宗成交，較上月多約三成，周末三天康怡花園睇樓預約睇樓量保持穩定。<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2841836?r=cpsdlc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2841836%3Fr%3Dcpsdlc&d=h8K6dYNnEA4rSgnLcindhePMooGStKW6IyA4tNg2jBs%3D&h=c86a0828\" target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2841836?r=cpsdlc</a><br />\nshortened and highlighted to aid reading"},{"pid":"a3ff7cee984db6e9c49c903ddd3c27cb858ea36d","tid":2348559,"uid":292362,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T20:02:57.000Z","msg":"gogogo <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b72ce914e1b4071b12b8b31bb8fac1e6f4009fe6","tid":2348559,"uid":4826,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T01:27:34.000Z","msg":"又升，冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c04d91b060ebfac5aac3